{"tid":1311194,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【安徽省猩猩爭自由】用竹翻牆「越獄」 起飛腳踢開管理員","createTime":"2019-07-13T05:22:53.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-14T07:05:24.000Z","uid":54733,"like":31,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"ab6ee2f6271b5aa7c5eb6499908b6dfa870c7aa2","tid":1311194,"uid":54733,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T05:22:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190713/large/1562987537_6d06.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190713%2Flarge%2F1562987537_6d06.jpg&h=0dae0713&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n黑猩猩翻牆「越獄」，起飛腳踢管理員。(互聯網)<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n安徽合肥野生動物園有一隻黑猩猩，為了爭取自由，昨日（12日）用竹子「翻牆」，企圖從欄舍逃出動物園時，更一腳踹飛一名管理員。<br />\n<br />\n這隻雄性黑猩猩名叫「陽陽」，今年12歲。牠昨日從欄舍逃離，並跑至動物園大門口，其間一名男員工與牠對峙，「陽陽」毫不留情一腳踹飛他。最後，園方報警要求協助，出動特警隊用麻醉槍將「陽陽」制服，目前園方已對黑猩猩注射解藥，動物園也暫時關閉，而被踹的男員工也沒有大礙。<br />\n<br />\n園方表示，「陽陽」利用竹子「翻牆」，成功逃離欄舍，目前已把牠安置在新欄舍內。據悉「陽陽」曾在2017年有脫逃紀錄，而且曾多次試圖逃跑，但最後都沒有成功。園方表示，黑猩猩看起來傻乎乎，但實際上是非常聰明的動物。"},{"pid":"28924edcebf7a84d633fbc26a6addf8c5bfa7526","tid":1311194,"uid":54733,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T05:23:21.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20190713/59818521\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190713%2F59818521&d=ev%2BvVaAtQ3cORw7W3wlzWc4e4tfxBia5339duguOAPM%3D&h=186f72e9\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190713%2F59818521&h=4c8d3520\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20190713/59818521</a>"},{"pid":"06d99581c0dd72a8629ae9fcdbf00a19964f9958","tid":1311194,"uid":54733,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T05:23:52.000Z","msg":"猩猩都識抗爭"},{"pid":"32e7c1843f6383547ec2d930facacbde52e0654f","tid":1311194,"uid":987,"like":7,"dislike":0